div.p:
The nationalities populating Roumania are: 1, Roumanians; 2, Greeks, Servians,
                    and Bulgarians; 3, Armenians, Lithuanians, and Gypsies; 4, Italians and French;
                    5, Hungarians, Germans, and Poles.

The working-power employed at agriculture are agriculture hands, 684, 168;
                    horses, 284,028; yoke-cattle, 961,973; wagons, 338,869; plows, 159,510;
                    machines, 2, 000.
